Debunking myths about how to avoid or cure coronavirus Social media is spreading plenty of false rumors about coronavirus.
Coronavirus, influenza and a common cold can present with cough and shortness of breath.
To start, according to the American Lung Foundation, lung fibrosis is scarring of the lung and can occur due to infections, medications, genetics or certain diseases.
